      },
      {
        "start": "03:44.200",
        "end": "03:47.300",
        "original": "Thank you for the encore, Ruffians!",
        "english": "Thank you for the encore, Ruffians!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:47.400",
        "end": "03:51.300",
        "original": "That was \"side by side\"! Bau bau!",
        "english": "That was \"side by side\"! Bau bau!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:52.100",
        "end": "03:56.500",
        "original": "We're really happy to perform \"side by side\" for the first time live today!",
        "english": "We're really happy to perform \"side by side\" for the first time live today!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:56.600",
        "end": "04:00.100",
        "original": "Yeah! 初披露できてとっても嬉しいです！",
        "english": "Yeah! I'm so happy we got to perform it for the first time!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:00.200",
        "end": "04:03.900",
        "original": "\"side by side\" is a song made by Alobahn-san, but also between FuwaMoco!",
        "english": "\"side by side\" is a song made by Alobahn-san, but also between FuwaMoco!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:04.000",
        "end": "04:07.400",
        "original": "Yeah, and us!",
        "english": "Yeah, and us!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:07.500",
        "end": "04:11.800",
        "original": "I know, we know it's a song that you love a lot,",
        "english": "I know, we know it's a song that you love a lot,",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:11.900",
        "end": "04:18.500",
        "original": "but we also do because it's very special to us since it's the ending theme for a visual novel that we care about!",
        "english": "but we also do because it's very special to us since it's the ending theme for a visual novel that we care about!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:18.600",
        "end": "04:19.400",
        "original": "Nekopara!",
        "english": "Nekopara!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:19.500",
        "end": "04:22.500",
        "original": "Nekopara! Bau bau!",
        "english": "Nekopara! Bau bau!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:22.600",
        "end": "04:30.000",
        "original": "And with this song, our dream of singing the opening or ending theme for a visual novel came true!",
        "english": "And with this song, our dream of singing the opening or ending theme for a visual novel came true!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:30.100",
        "end": "04:36.100",
        "original": "Yeah! そう、この曲でフワモコの夢、美少女ゲームの主題歌を歌うことが叶いました！",
        "english": "Yeah! That's right, with this song, FuwaMoco's dream of singing a bishojo game theme song has come true!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:36.200",
        "end": "04:40.400",
        "original": "Yeah, it came true! Thank you!",
        "english": "Yeah, it came true! Thank you!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:40.500",
        "end": "04:41.200",
        "original": "Thank you!",
        "english": "Thank you!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:41.300",
        "end": "04:43.700",
        "original": "ありがとう！",
        "english": "Thank you!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "04:43.800",
        "end": "04:48.300",
        "original": "And thank you so much for joining us for our special day again this year!",
        "english": "And thank you so much for joining us for our special day again this year!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
